@NODE History "Release History"

3.0  2006-11-17  Ported to AmigaOS 4.0
                 Moved prefs file from S:docket.data to ENVARC:docket.prefs
                 Consolidated version strings
                 Commands are executed with NIL: in/out/err streams
                 Cancelled items no longer remain in the list
                 Added command test button
                 Now optimizes executable

2.0  1997-09-13  First public release.
                 Designed as a commodity.

1.0  1997-02-08  Private release.
                 Designed as a preference program and a daemon.
@ENDNODE


@NODE Future "Future of Amiga Docket"

Development of Docket will continue as long as I have a need for it.

Possible things to do to Amiga Docket Preferences:
 1. Provide control over the stack.
 2. Add built-in commands for items such as message display and sounding.
 3. Sort the list of items according to item type.
